    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dams oriented in the direction of the flow of a river, as protection for hollow river banks or of bridge piers, or for limiting the river's normal width.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
